Class LatLngBounds

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fujion.ancillary.Options
      • org.fujion.gmaps.LatLngBounds
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OptionMap.IOptionMapConverter, IClientTransform

    public class LatLngBounds
extends Options
    Represents a rectangle in geographical coordinates, including one that crosses the 180 degrees longitudinal meridian.
